PHOTO FILTERS PACK 1.0 - ELECTION
We’ve introduced filters for your profile photos with this update! What better way to kick off filters than with a subject matter that is already a daily discussion - the US Presidential Primary Election. We’ll be adding more filter packs frequently so you can get a better idea of what each person you’re swiping on stands for at just a glance.

ALSO…
General bug fixes and beekeeping.

LIKING IN CHAT
Tired of trying to figure out how to acknowledge someone's clever message with a quick reply? Now you can tap the yellow heart next to a message to let your connection know how great they are.

ALSO...

BUMBLE BOOST
You’re a busy bee and your time is valuable. Upgrade to Bumble Boost to meet, date, and friend people faster and easier than ever. Buy back expired connections, gain access to unlimited 24 hour extensions, and make a “beeline” to quicker matches by sorting through people who have already swiped right on you. 

BUMBLE + SPOTIFY
Music connects us. Now find out more about the people on Bumble through their top artists on Spotify! To connect your top artists, go to your profile, click on the edit button, and scroll down to select Spotify. 

BUMBLE BFF
It feels easier to find a date than to find a friend, right? Not anymore! With BumbleBFF, it’s easy. To swipe through new friends and expand your squad in your area, go to settings, and under preferences select “BumbleBFF." You'll be Bumble Friends Forever.

ALSO...
Behind the scene fixes and general beekeeping.

INTRODUCING MODE SWITCHING 

This new feature allows you to seamlessly switch between Bumble and Bumble BFF mode empowering you to make the connections you want to make--on a single social networking platform. 

Already in a relationship but looking to make new friends? Find your best man or wing-woman on Bumble BFF! Build out a separate Bumble BFF profile and start filling your life with people who will help you make new memories!

INTRODUCING BUMBLE BIZZ 

This new mode within the Bumble app transforms the way both brands and users network, develop new career opportunities, and find mentoring and mentorship possibilities. With Bizz, every swipe you make is an opportunity to expand your professional landscape and make empowered career moves. 

MODE SWITCHING

This new feature allows you to seamlessly switch between Bumble, Bumble BFF, and Bumble Bizz—empowering you to make the connections you want to make in a single social networking platform. Looking to use Bumble for dating and networking connections? Mode switching allows you to manage up to three separate profiles to make sure no accidents happen.

INTRODUCING THE INSTAGRAM FEED

Share your recent Instagram posts on your Bumble profile! In addition to seeing users’ profile pictures, you’ll now be able to browse through Instagram photos to get to know people (and their photo taking skills) before deciding to connect. Don't worry, Bumble won't share your handle or link out to your feed, so your information is secure!
